{"title":"用AI玩转3D动效设计","slug":"frstou1o7ggx43cy","summary":"原文链接： https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkxMjI3Mjg2NQ==&amp;mid=2247487094&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=f83a12c660524b01db1fd6feee81e978&amp;scene=21&am","category":"8. 用AI做动效设计","tags":["PART7️⃣ 设计全流程AI提效指南","8. 用AI做动效设计"],"featured":false,"order":117,"level":2,"updatedAt":"2026-01-03","wordCount":2680,"sourceUrl":"https://www.yuque.com/abyssalsailor/yg90qa/frstou1o7ggx43cy","html":"<blockquote data-lake-id=\"ue47f9bd3\" id=\"ue47f9bd3\"><p data-lake-id=\"u28ba308c\" id=\"u28ba308c\"><span data-lake-id=\"ue241502a\" id=\"ue241502a\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">原文链接：</span><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkxMjI3Mjg2NQ==&amp;mid=2247487094&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=f83a12c660524b01db1fd6feee81e978&amp;scene=21&amp;poc_token=HPy3kGij_gjAy3apPL2H2bibJosyG4cZ6LfNquxI\" target=\"_blank\" data-lake-id=\"u7fe4dcbd\" id=\"u7fe4dcbd\"><span data-lake-id=\"uda1a059e\" id=\"uda1a059e\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkxMjI3Mjg2NQ==&amp;mid=2247487094&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=f83a12c660524b01db1fd6feee81e978&amp;scene=21&amp;poc_token=HPy3kGij_gjAy3apPL2H2bibJosyG4cZ6LfNquxI</span></a></p><p data-lake-id=\"u01492784\" id=\"u01492784\"><span data-lake-id=\"uf136991a\" id=\"uf136991a\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">图文来源：阿里健康设计</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"uf3336975\" id=\"uf3336975\"><span data-lake-id=\"uc2962f46\" id=\"uc2962f46\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">作者：如稷</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u651688f1\" id=\"u651688f1\"><span data-lake-id=\"ud3f7d968\" id=\"ud3f7d968\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">版权归作者所有</span></p></blockquote><p data-lake-id=\"uc0ef6013\" id=\"uc0ef6013\" class=\"lake-lineheight-115\"><span data-lake-id=\"u37541406\" id=\"u37541406\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">​</span><br></p><p data-lake-id=\"u3445bf5d\" id=\"u3445bf5d\" class=\"lake-lineheight-115\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"ub85b320d\" id=\"ub85b320d\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">当Sketch遇上AIGC动效工具，设计师的加班时代正在终结，生成动态的界面动效，这波生产力革命你赶上了吗？</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"ubc6c6049\" id=\"ubc6c6049\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fwebp%2F1206632%2F1754314852232-d7f49e99-6b06-4c20-a5f1-5f84be4fd648.webp%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u15d6b622-ee0e-4fe6-b436-392bc04f3df%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u48340898-cef7-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22width%22%3A960%2C%22height%22%3A540%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1080%2C%22originHeight%22%3A608%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23cee1c8%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u54b575ce%22%7D\"></card></p><h2 data-lake-id=\"4fcd93df\" id=\"4fcd93df\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ue3660b95\" id=\"ue3660b95\" class=\"lake-fontsize-18\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(61, 167, 66)\">1. 引言 </span></strong></h2><p data-lake-id=\"u662788c7\" id=\"u662788c7\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"u8f3fd2f2\" id=\"u8f3fd2f2\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">AIGC是这几年最大的创意红利，我在项目里首次接触AIGC，通过短期的技术摸索沉淀，结合各个模型的特征和利弊，在短短的一周之内同时需要完成多线任务的情况下，最大程度实现了AI在“创作控制”和“落地项目”的平衡，对于画面的艺术性和趣味性，品牌的张力上，都力求达成一份完美的AI融合。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"ua07dd3b1\" id=\"ua07dd3b1\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"u3f74a02c\" id=\"u3f74a02c\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">参与的减重战役项目中，通过借助AI技术高效生成风格统一且情感共鸣的动效素材，智能展现人物形象及动态瘦身效果，增强用户减重信心。实践表明，动效生成周期缩短70%，验证AIGC在界面动效的有效应用。分享一个最近做的典型案例，具体需求如下图：</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u1afbc4e3\" id=\"u1afbc4e3\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fwebp%2F1206632%2F1754314851537-2211ef9c-afef-4ec0-b207-69b66ab60ef1.webp%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u0fb2b7b7-f071-453f-8ef2-73238c0c547%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u48340898-cef7-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22width%22%3A1920%2C%22height%22%3A1081%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1080%2C%22originHeight%22%3A608%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23f6f6f5%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u93dda50f%22%7D\"></card></p><h2 data-lake-id=\"f0NBR\" id=\"f0NBR\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"uf3e3e01b\" id=\"uf3e3e01b\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\"><br /><br /></span></h2><h2 data-lake-id=\"70a68922\" id=\"70a68922\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"uef1eb8ba\" id=\"uef1eb8ba\" class=\"lake-fontsize-18\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(61, 167, 66)\">2. 准备工作 </span></strong></h2><h3 data-lake-id=\"a3339d8f\" id=\"a3339d8f\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ua55a4a63\" id=\"ua55a4a63\" class=\"lake-fontsize-14\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 180, 80)\">动效脚本设计</span></strong></h3><p data-lake-id=\"ubb4d45fe\" id=\"ubb4d45fe\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"u101d194d\" id=\"u101d194d\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">如何通过动态素材去表达合适的减重主题，就需要通过对画面元素的合理拆解，提炼AI可覆盖的素材生成，制定相应动画素材生成策略。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u00045c8a\" id=\"u00045c8a\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fwebp%2F1206632%2F1754314851617-4181f8b3-f93e-4e83-a2ab-0c4858a07f1e.webp%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22udea7b2a2-93e5-471b-be01-ca819e9bc12%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u48340898-cef7-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22width%22%3A1920%2C%22height%22%3A1081%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1080%2C%22originHeight%22%3A608%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23f7f6f5%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u80f821d4%22%7D\"></card></p><h3 data-lake-id=\"e5cd56fb\" id=\"e5cd56fb\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u825df470\" id=\"u825df470\" class=\"lake-fontsize-14\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 180, 80)\">工具测评</span></strong></h3><p data-lake-id=\"u4c7c2862\" id=\"u4c7c2862\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"u6205f9c6\" id=\"u6205f9c6\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">对当前流行的图片生成AI工具进行了测评并总结如下：</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"ue4e859b5\" id=\"ue4e859b5\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fwebp%2F1206632%2F1754314851958-12fd45f9-2a41-4a79-8789-7d4d6afedea5.webp%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u25cdc9aa-b738-40ce-b89e-934b6a7d0ab%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u48340898-cef7-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22width%22%3A1920%2C%22height%22%3A825%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1080%2C%22originHeight%22%3A464%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23fbfbfb%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22ue8fcf6c3%22%7D\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"u83dbed68\" id=\"u83dbed68\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ucd304711\" id=\"ucd304711\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">生图表现：</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u5d576cb4\" id=\"u5d576cb4\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">Chatgpt是我测评所有的生图软件里比较高效的快速的软件，他的优势很明显，在所有的生图软件里，优势为听得懂人话，具备兜底的设计能力。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u475e0d91\" id=\"u475e0d91\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u159bf250\" id=\"u159bf250\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">动态视频表现：可灵</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u3c637cc1\" id=\"u3c637cc1\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">视频表现令人惊叹，无论是被诟病的手部动作（“Ai不会画手”），还是人物的表情变化，可灵都处理得相当出色。尤其是近景特写，没有明显的Bug。</span></p><h2 data-lake-id=\"-1\" id=\"-1\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"u302616a5\" id=\"u302616a5\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\"><br /><br /></span></h2><h2 data-lake-id=\"f74a6ced\" id=\"f74a6ced\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ud4794229\" id=\"ud4794229\" class=\"lake-fontsize-18\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(61, 167, 66)\">3. 动效SOP工作流说明 </span></strong></h2><p data-lake-id=\"u49d6212e\" id=\"u49d6212e\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"uf77c1f14\" id=\"uf77c1f14\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">经过项目的复盘，总结了一套生成动效的SOP，主要分为4个步骤，包含生成分镜素材、合成动态视频、视频细节调整、落地输出。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u204fe216\" id=\"u204fe216\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"udffe7362\" id=\"udffe7362\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\"><br /><br /></span></strong></p><p data-lake-id=\"u290aa7ec\" id=\"u290aa7ec\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u2523f3ef\" id=\"u2523f3ef\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 180, 80)\">工具推荐</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u69e5f091\" id=\"u69e5f091\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\"><br /><br /></span></p><p data-lake-id=\"ua7edd9ca\" id=\"ua7edd9ca\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"ud7afbc4c\" id=\"ud7afbc4c\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">Chatgpt（需要购置会员）、可灵（有新人赠券+购置会员）、Photoshop、Adobe After Effects</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"uea173975\" id=\"uea173975\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fwebp%2F1206632%2F1754314852221-83926326-b01d-48fa-85c6-2ccd4e7aa95b.webp%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u638325fb-f8ca-4307-bceb-7c5aa5fc11f%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u48340898-cef7-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22width%22%3A1920%2C%22height%22%3A1081%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1080%2C%22originHeight%22%3A608%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%239bcd8a%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u96012b7c%22%7D\"></card></p><h2 data-lake-id=\"8b69d151\" id=\"8b69d151\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ud2e116b2\" id=\"ud2e116b2\" class=\"lake-fontsize-14\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 180, 80)\">SOP-1 生成分镜素材</span></strong></h2><p data-lake-id=\"u78722668\" id=\"u78722668\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"ucc18068a\" id=\"ucc18068a\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">制作减重动效需要人物素材，因此通过找参考、垫图换衣服、垫图换脸等方法生成人物基底角色形象图，然后基于基底图生成胖瘦的两个状态（形象+动作），通过对基底图进行垫图来保证胖瘦形象的一致。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"ud192119f\" id=\"ud192119f\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"u9a29a7db\" id=\"u9a29a7db\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">以下为通过chatgpt垫图生成基底图及胖瘦两个状态的静态图片素材，作为后期视频合成的素材。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"ucc9268ad\" id=\"ucc9268ad\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fwebp%2F1206632%2F1754314853423-32538ad0-974f-4d7a-a9da-4c43c7efebfe.webp%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u2476ffd7-d33a-438e-9b77-13ccb6ced76%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u48340898-cef7-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22width%22%3A2095%2C%22height%22%3A1280%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1080%2C%22originHeight%22%3A660%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23f7f6f5%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u2b9ba850%22%7D\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"u9d41d3f5\" id=\"u9d41d3f5\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"ub266f523\" id=\"ub266f523\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">用到3个镜头的素材，用基底生成胖、瘦两个动作</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"uc506bb35\" id=\"uc506bb35\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fwebp%2F1206632%2F1754314853447-b13dd259-894a-4f50-b3b4-2bafd2016f14.webp%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u671680f6-4b25-41f0-8ba7-d3f580267a6%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u48340898-cef7-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22width%22%3A1920%2C%22height%22%3A811%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1080%2C%22originHeight%22%3A456%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23f5f1ec%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u29f3ceac%22%7D\"></card></p><h2 data-lake-id=\"bc14bd21\" id=\"bc14bd21\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u7b9dbe82\" id=\"u7b9dbe82\" class=\"lake-fontsize-14\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 180, 80)\">SOP-2 合成动态素材</span></strong></h2><h3 data-lake-id=\"cf0bef70\" id=\"cf0bef70\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u3c79a1d3\" id=\"u3c79a1d3\" class=\"lake-fontsize-14\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">合成素材探索案例尝试</span></strong></h3><p data-lake-id=\"u95bc0552\" id=\"u95bc0552\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"u2467129f\" id=\"u2467129f\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">综合测评中，因可灵支持「文生视频」、「图生视频」以及「首尾帧」，所以选为生成视频的工具。</span></p><ul list=\"ud47a37fd\"><li fid=\"u03d9eb8a\" data-lake-id=\"uf02859bc\" id=\"uf02859bc\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"u2d1d2309\" id=\"u2d1d2309\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">可设置多种参数来控制视频生成效果：包括运镜控制、生成模式（高性能、高表现）、添加尾帧、想象力及相关性控制等，最长可延长视频至10分钟。</span></li><li fid=\"u03d9eb8a\" data-lake-id=\"u5d7b4ea9\" id=\"u5d7b4ea9\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"uc57ec1dc\" id=\"uc57ec1dc\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">首尾帧：可灵目前还没有控制变量（控制随机种子）的功能，若觉得生成的视频效果还不错，想在此基础上保留原有效果再生成一段类似效果，只能重新抽卡。测试下来可灵中的「首尾帧」是可控性比较强的模型，可以通过首张首尾两帧图作为定量，加以中间的转场动效完成转变，因此需要利用这个特性完成项目。</span></li></ul><p data-lake-id=\"u4be09282\" id=\"u4be09282\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"u07900c95\" id=\"u07900c95\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">在合成视频中，尝试了多种提示词，发现提示词的结构很大程度上会决定效果成败，因此在摸索中不断找到合适的提示词公式，自后提炼出提示词公式，我们来看一下探索过程中的案例，希望对你如何生成动态视频素材提供参考价值，以及给到我实践下来针对项目比较合适的提示词公式。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"ufb5ef4f2\" id=\"ufb5ef4f2\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"u262c9a94\" id=\"u262c9a94\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">接下来开始进行合成动态素材的操作步骤，如下图：</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"ucb6558aa\" id=\"ucb6558aa\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fwebp%2F1206632%2F1754314853494-2d44685f-e7f4-4fb2-9852-f04d0115e7b4.webp%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u84334622-a9a2-46d0-a41b-87cde3b9979%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u48340898-cef7-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22width%22%3A1920%2C%22height%22%3A1081%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1080%2C%22originHeight%22%3A608%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%2386ca73%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u0868040e%22%7D\"></card></p><h3 data-lake-id=\"7d351bff\" id=\"7d351bff\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u46f89087\" id=\"u46f89087\" class=\"lake-fontsize-14\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">案例一</span></strong></h3><p data-lake-id=\"u1bd218b2\" id=\"u1bd218b2\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fwebp%2F1206632%2F1754314853499-fe37b009-ca50-4ba9-936d-40df6ef86096.webp%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u467e13bd-745b-479e-a155-db3332ec9f8%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u48340898-cef7-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22width%22%3A465%2C%22height%22%3A260%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A930%2C%22originHeight%22%3A520%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23f3f0e5%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22uc7bf15e9%22%7D\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"u2256bfcc\" id=\"u2256bfcc\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"uf6a637f6\" id=\"uf6a637f6\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">提示词：</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"uc084c7df\" id=\"uc084c7df\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">两位卡通人物在运动场中同步进行网球挥拍与室内骑行蹬踏，左侧人物挥动绿色网球拍击打弹跳的网球，右侧人物规律地蹬踏健身车车轮旋转，固定镜头展现夸张肢体动作与趣味互动。右侧人物男生和左侧人物女生，同时顺时针缓慢转圈一周，身体从肥胖逐渐变瘦，全身散发白色粒子闪光，透明背景，8K高清，电影质感。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u7ec963c0\" id=\"u7ec963c0\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"uc61718ac\" id=\"uc61718ac\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">思考：</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u2a3f5e96\" id=\"u2a3f5e96\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">避免动作复杂，避免多人运动，提示词的从句比较多，AI难以理解。需要再次优化提示词。优化思路：尝试换成1个人去做动作，单人做动作控制，要比双人效果的效果好一些，但是还是会出现羽毛球拍的扭曲和变形。旋转的提示词要明确，是原地旋转还是转一圈旋转，旋转的角度和头身的变化。</span></p><h3 data-lake-id=\"-2\" id=\"-2\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ubca20a1a\" id=\"ubca20a1a\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\"><br /><br /></span></strong></h3><h3 data-lake-id=\"55c5026a\" id=\"55c5026a\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u5478c2dc\" id=\"u5478c2dc\" class=\"lake-fontsize-14\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">案例二</span></strong></h3><p data-lake-id=\"uc4437810\" id=\"uc4437810\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fwebp%2F1206632%2F1754314854234-b75dd24b-dba7-4bd9-8b01-8e7e919ff16f.webp%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u39caf81d-b981-4148-a2d7-0b34a389cd2%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u48340898-cef7-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22width%22%3A465%2C%22height%22%3A260%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A930%2C%22originHeight%22%3A520%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23f6f0ec%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u130c7e38%22%7D\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"ue6411ec3\" id=\"ue6411ec3\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"uf7ff23a3\" id=\"uf7ff23a3\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">提示词</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u2fd48be1\" id=\"u2fd48be1\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">：一位微胖的女性，身穿白色运动T恤和绿色运动短裤，保持叉腰动作在原地旋转360度，身材从微胖到瘦，身材逐渐变得苗条，用时1.5秒。转完圈以后变瘦同时两手张开，固定镜头3秒。头绳为深草绿色跟裤子同色。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u1e2a17ce\" id=\"u1e2a17ce\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u33596350\" id=\"u33596350\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">不希望呈现的内容：</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"udb518154\" id=\"udb518154\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">变形、面部表情、不必要的动作、跳跃、摆动</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u388e4f37\" id=\"u388e4f37\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u8927db5c\" id=\"u8927db5c\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">思考：</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"ue451b804\" id=\"ue451b804\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">提示词描述的前后顺序跟着动画的帧数前后顺序变化，改变动作前后的顺序，避免长句，动作拆解变化要跟着帧的前后关系走，方便AI通过短句理解并完成动态前后变化素材准确生成。</span></p><h3 data-lake-id=\"-3\" id=\"-3\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ua9913d21\" id=\"ua9913d21\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\"><br /><br /></span></strong></h3><h3 data-lake-id=\"729d207a\" id=\"729d207a\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"uc0005c25\" id=\"uc0005c25\" class=\"lake-fontsize-14\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">案例三</span></strong></h3><p data-lake-id=\"uc16296e1\" id=\"uc16296e1\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fwebp%2F1206632%2F1754314854841-6e54d8a1-ee91-4a10-adf9-34b0021e6256.webp%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u672e87ee-6932-4ac3-b2db-1f9e79c3b4d%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u48340898-cef7-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22width%22%3A465%2C%22height%22%3A260%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A930%2C%22originHeight%22%3A520%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23f6f0ec%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u2c38cf7e%22%7D\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"u1a0960af\" id=\"u1a0960af\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"u1657961e\" id=\"u1657961e\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">提示词：一位微胖的女性，身穿白色运动T恤和绿色运动短裤，身材从微胖到瘦且原地旋转360度用时1.5秒。变瘦完成后固定镜头3秒。头绳为深草绿色跟裤子同色。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u9139b6dc\" id=\"u9139b6dc\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u35125bd4\" id=\"u35125bd4\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">思考：</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"ue5beee5f\" id=\"ue5beee5f\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">该视频比较符合预期目标，并且发现提示词的基本规律满足公式 </span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u70ad3d48\" id=\"u70ad3d48\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\">Prompt=主体（主体描述）+运动+视角+（镜头语言+面部表情）。</span></strong></p><h3 data-lake-id=\"-4\" id=\"-4\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u3dc33199\" id=\"u3dc33199\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\"><br /><br /></span></strong></h3><h3 data-lake-id=\"8bd79ed4\" id=\"8bd79ed4\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u61f76843\" id=\"u61f76843\" class=\"lake-fontsize-14\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">案例四</span></strong></h3><p data-lake-id=\"u00ca0861\" id=\"u00ca0861\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fwebp%2F1206632%2F1754314854310-2de08ce0-b2e2-4457-9ce3-1af467168ed7.webp%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22ua38d2abc-788d-4f7a-8f40-9447fdbb5a1%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u48340898-cef7-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22width%22%3A465%2C%22height%22%3A260%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A930%2C%22originHeight%22%3A520%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23fbf8f4%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22ue1f423a1%22%7D\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"ub358e576\" id=\"ub358e576\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u7ca39920\" id=\"u7ca39920\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">提示词：</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u029ba12c\" id=\"u029ba12c\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">一位微胖男性，身穿运动服和绿色运动短裤静止站1秒，摇摆身体用时1.5秒慢慢变得苗条，固定姿态定格静止3秒并挥手摇摆比肌肉。固定镜头。</span></p><h3 data-lake-id=\"4c2acc50\" id=\"4c2acc50\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><u><span data-lake-id=\"u201e0759\" id=\"u201e0759\" class=\"lake-fontsize-14\">总结提示词公式</span></u></span></strong></h3><p data-lake-id=\"u2fda5c63\" id=\"u2fda5c63\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ua33bd98f\" id=\"ua33bd98f\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">动效提示词公式=【主体】+【主体描述】+【视角】+【镜头语言】+【面部表情】</span></strong></p><ul list=\"u994e9d97\"><li fid=\"ua26ad009\" data-lake-id=\"ua04251da\" id=\"ua04251da\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"u4fb71249\" id=\"u4fb71249\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">一致性：用</span><code data-lake-id=\"uce2e4eea\" id=\"uce2e4eea\"><span data-lake-id=\"ua49a5461\" id=\"ua49a5461\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06)\">同一人物</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u7915c6d9\" id=\"u7915c6d9\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">、</span><code data-lake-id=\"udf93aa7f\" id=\"udf93aa7f\"><span data-lake-id=\"u1cf3fa86\" id=\"u1cf3fa86\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06)\">相同服装</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"ua035a223\" id=\"ua035a223\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">等词锁定角色特征，避免变形错乱。</span></li><li fid=\"ua26ad009\" data-lake-id=\"u1654ba28\" id=\"u1654ba28\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"u93249cbe\" id=\"u93249cbe\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">动态强化</span><span data-lake-id=\"ub9daffdb\" id=\"ub9daffdb\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">：加入如</span><code data-lake-id=\"uc1d47130\" id=\"uc1d47130\"><span data-lake-id=\"u4c7da051\" id=\"u4c7da051\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06)\">发丝飘动</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u500551db\" id=\"u500551db\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">、</span><code data-lake-id=\"u8ce286cb\" id=\"u8ce286cb\"><span data-lake-id=\"u5d967fe1\" id=\"u5d967fe1\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06)\">衣摆飞扬</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u7721e55e\" id=\"u7721e55e\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">等细节增强动感。</span></li><li fid=\"ua26ad009\" data-lake-id=\"u01e05675\" id=\"u01e05675\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"u7a711631\" id=\"u7a711631\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">时间控制：通过</span><code data-lake-id=\"u790327f8\" id=\"u790327f8\"><span data-lake-id=\"u3dc85fdf\" id=\"u3dc85fdf\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06)\">0.5秒过渡</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"ubd3cfeee\" id=\"ubd3cfeee\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">、</span><code data-lake-id=\"uad9d035a\" id=\"uad9d035a\"><span data-lake-id=\"u69526267\" id=\"u69526267\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06)\">首尾各1秒</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"uff1c59ec\" id=\"uff1c59ec\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">指定时长。</span></li><li fid=\"ua26ad009\" data-lake-id=\"u9e03077f\" id=\"u9e03077f\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"uded967dc\" id=\"uded967dc\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">简化描述：避免复杂从句，用逗号分隔短句，提高AI识别率。</span></li></ul><p data-lake-id=\"ubfa9919e\" id=\"ubfa9919e\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fwebp%2F1206632%2F1754314854370-6183ec04-dc33-4196-81b6-53dc62d0a7a9.webp%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22ud0d3d6d6-5ebf-4823-9f68-78e2b140ba5%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u48340898-cef7-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22width%22%3A1920%2C%22height%22%3A1081%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1080%2C%22originHeight%22%3A608%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23f2f2f2%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u475c0b6d%22%7D\"></card></p><h2 data-lake-id=\"-5\" id=\"-5\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"u66aa9bfb\" id=\"u66aa9bfb\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\"><br /><br /></span></h2><h2 data-lake-id=\"e53f56ec\" id=\"e53f56ec\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ufd4b574b\" id=\"ufd4b574b\" class=\"lake-fontsize-14\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 180, 80)\">SOP-3 AI生成素材细节调整</span></strong></h2><p data-lake-id=\"u9eda4d6a\" id=\"u9eda4d6a\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"u6bf31749\" id=\"u6bf31749\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">为了能够对视频细节进行调整，需要将生成的AI视频苏词啊导入到ps中做细节处理，其中包括视频中不需要展示的某些帧数、时长调整以及背景透明的批量化处理。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u486d6a01\" id=\"u486d6a01\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u62dc8d71\" id=\"u62dc8d71\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">① 文件导入</span></strong></p><ul list=\"ua4317bfd\"><li fid=\"u5c5ddeb8\" data-lake-id=\"u92c280b1\" id=\"u92c280b1\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ub596818e\" id=\"ub596818e\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">文件/导入/视频帧到图层</span></strong></li><li fid=\"u5c5ddeb8\" data-lake-id=\"u1cb8a7fb\" id=\"u1cb8a7fb\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"ue94d1f5f\" id=\"ue94d1f5f\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">选中导入视频素材/打开</span></li><li fid=\"u5c5ddeb8\" data-lake-id=\"ud8d3e5aa\" id=\"ud8d3e5aa\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"uca8318bd\" id=\"uca8318bd\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">将视频导入图层/默认选项/确定</span></li></ul><p data-lake-id=\"u2abb88e2\" id=\"u2abb88e2\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u1d96dfb3\" id=\"u1d96dfb3\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">② 设置时间轴</span></strong></p><ul list=\"u31458e2d\"><li fid=\"ue8684cec\" data-lake-id=\"u987f25b9\" id=\"u987f25b9\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"u9b03a253\" id=\"u9b03a253\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">点击窗口/时间轴</span></li><li fid=\"ue8684cec\" data-lake-id=\"u7e5f2ecc\" id=\"u7e5f2ecc\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"u814335e2\" id=\"u814335e2\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">图层帧选择无延迟</span></li></ul><p data-lake-id=\"ubd09b70f\" id=\"ubd09b70f\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u07a8655a\" id=\"u07a8655a\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">③ 对素材细节进行微调&amp;批量化处理</span></strong></p><ul list=\"u23aa5571\"><li fid=\"u88721d46\" data-lake-id=\"ue9324377\" id=\"ue9324377\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"ub178756f\" id=\"ub178756f\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">对不必要的视频内容进行删帧</span></li><li fid=\"u88721d46\" data-lake-id=\"u1743a1eb\" id=\"u1743a1eb\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"udd4b24b6\" id=\"udd4b24b6\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">对图层进行背景透明化批量操作</span></li><li fid=\"u88721d46\" data-lake-id=\"u7a6f0d77\" id=\"u7a6f0d77\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"ue32a7d8d\" id=\"ue32a7d8d\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">将时间轴转换为视频时间轴</span></li></ul><p data-lake-id=\"u12fc3007\" id=\"u12fc3007\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"uf0bf413b\" id=\"uf0bf413b\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">④ 输出GIF</span></strong></p><ul list=\"ubdf668c7\"><li fid=\"ue74c7771\" data-lake-id=\"u799162d7\" id=\"u799162d7\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"u849a2d7e\" id=\"u849a2d7e\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">将时间轴转换为视频时间轴</span></li><li fid=\"ue74c7771\" data-lake-id=\"u86bd3ce1\" id=\"u86bd3ce1\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"u3ba701c2\" id=\"u3ba701c2\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">保存Web所用格式（旧版）</span></li></ul><p data-lake-id=\"u46ff2e00\" id=\"u46ff2e00\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fwebp%2F1206632%2F1754314854992-ac027905-0ed8-42a8-838c-0a9d2af2f050.webp%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22ubd6fab44-8809-4643-9829-476cf71f0de%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u48340898-cef7-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22width%22%3A1920%2C%22height%22%3A1120%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1080%2C%22originHeight%22%3A630%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23c4c3c2%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22uf5b8a38b%22%7D\"></card></p><h2 data-lake-id=\"-6\" id=\"-6\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"u5427477e\" id=\"u5427477e\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\"><br /><br /></span></h2><h2 data-lake-id=\"dc460a6b\" id=\"dc460a6b\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ufee0d638\" id=\"ufee0d638\" class=\"lake-fontsize-14\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 180, 80)\">SOP-4 落地输出</span></strong></h2><h3 data-lake-id=\"bd5df1d6\" id=\"bd5df1d6\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u21e56d66\" id=\"u21e56d66\" class=\"lake-fontsize-14\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">AE：视频细节进一步调整&amp;输出PNG格式</span></strong></h3><p data-lake-id=\"u1f56aa07\" id=\"u1f56aa07\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"ue0881892\" id=\"ue0881892\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">素材导入到AE里再做细节的进一步调整，导入AE中做微调和输出处理，添加装饰元素，按照导出切图的大小给到开发。其中AE中关键帧的打法的教程网上有很多，大家比较熟悉就不赘述，仅做流程步骤的阐述。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"uc5e76535\" id=\"uc5e76535\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fwebp%2F1206632%2F1754314855219-2ff68393-0dc7-4e40-ada9-c8a49036841f.webp%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22ue9c971a0-b727-4a67-ad63-f74bb5d3a28%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u48340898-cef7-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22width%22%3A960%2C%22height%22%3A401%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1080%2C%22originHeight%22%3A451%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%231d1b19%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u533fda8f%22%7D\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"u4aa3b1ae\" id=\"u4aa3b1ae\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fwebp%2F1206632%2F1754314855193-df32879f-3a60-40cc-aa9c-49004551f36e.webp%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22ucfe393d3-93db-487d-80f7-61c2e57fa5b%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u48340898-cef7-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22width%22%3A1920%2C%22height%22%3A2395%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1080%2C%22originHeight%22%3A1347%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%237c7c7b%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22uc3bc37a9%22%7D\"></card></p><h3 data-lake-id=\"2a3b39d9\" id=\"2a3b39d9\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"u9602a11e\" id=\"u9602a11e\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">PS：将AE生成的图层导入到PS中进行GIF格式转换并导出</span></h3><p data-lake-id=\"ua0573b0a\" id=\"ua0573b0a\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fwebp%2F1206632%2F1754314855585-602a4674-48a5-4467-82f0-4047fd6e8c02.webp%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u60a14850-714b-4125-9501-ecc03a134d1%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u48340898-cef7-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22width%22%3A960%2C%22height%22%3A401%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1080%2C%22originHeight%22%3A451%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23363433%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u8c448886%22%7D\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"ub15ce080\" id=\"ub15ce080\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"u65d11552\" id=\"u65d11552\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">因为需要将AE生成的动态视频转换成GIF格式，所以需要把素材导入ps进行进一步的输出。操作步骤如下：</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u93e2637f\" id=\"u93e2637f\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"u8c5b0501\" id=\"u8c5b0501\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">① 选择【脚本】选择【将文件载入堆栈】</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"uad00bfde\" id=\"uad00bfde\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"u1c920dca\" id=\"u1c920dca\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">② 创建时间轴</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u76ebe32f\" id=\"u76ebe32f\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"ufe18c714\" id=\"ufe18c714\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">③ 转换帧-转换视频动画</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"ubb7922eb\" id=\"ubb7922eb\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"u4bd7812d\" id=\"u4bd7812d\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">④ 从图层建立帧</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"ufe149315\" id=\"ufe149315\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"uaa871a24\" id=\"uaa871a24\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">⑤ 反向帧</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u73e534c9\" id=\"u73e534c9\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"u65fabbcf\" id=\"u65fabbcf\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">⑥ 转换为视频时间轴</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u1a09e96c\" id=\"u1a09e96c\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"u7b0e50f4\" id=\"u7b0e50f4\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">⑦ 导出-存储为web所用格式（旧版）</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u68bac13b\" id=\"u68bac13b\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fwebp%2F1206632%2F1754314855984-3af9dce6-3a54-4396-aa60-e4675ee75077.webp%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22uc5010af3-a5b8-4dfe-8ed6-567ce91be9f%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u48340898-cef7-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22width%22%3A1920%2C%22height%22%3A1932%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1080%2C%22originHeight%22%3A1087%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23999796%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u8f45879a%22%7D\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"ubfb7d181\" id=\"ubfb7d181\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"u731d8ac0\" id=\"u731d8ac0\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\"><br /><br /></span></p><h2 data-lake-id=\"ea15281c\" id=\"ea15281c\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u0c39a84c\" id=\"u0c39a84c\" class=\"lake-fontsize-18\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(61, 167, 66)\">4. 对于应用AI动效的思考 </span></strong></h2><p data-lake-id=\"u5434ef53\" id=\"u5434ef53\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"ud47fafbe\" id=\"ud47fafbe\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">该项目总结出来的3D动效SOP工作流，可以广泛扩展到私域其他场景，动态素材的扩展场景应用举例如下图：</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u41b3053f\" id=\"u41b3053f\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fwebp%2F1206632%2F1754314856013-c82166bf-58b2-40ac-913c-24ee7c608cf1.webp%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u7429ceac-cbc8-45f3-97d1-ee8accc4072%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u48340898-cef7-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22width%22%3A960%2C%22height%22%3A540%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1080%2C%22originHeight%22%3A608%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23e0d7d3%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22ua9a5118c%22%7D\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"u3ebd6ad2\" id=\"u3ebd6ad2\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"uba146d4e\" id=\"uba146d4e\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">AI作为超级助手，提升了设计师效率，却无法替代其核心创意与动效的情感叙事掌控力，如同CGI取代不了导演。</span></p>"}
